place the knife inside the cabinet above the microwave which is above the stove, but place it in a green cup
pick up the green up from out of the cabinet above the microwave

high_descs: Walk to the counter on the right.
Pick up the knife in front of the sink on the left side on the counter.
Turn around, head left, hang a left at the windows, turn left, walk to the stove on the right and look up at the microwave.
Open the upper cabinets and put the knife inside the green glass on the left side.
Pick up the green glass with the knife inside and close the doors.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on the left.
Put the glass with the knife inside on the counter to the left of the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step to your left then walk to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the butter knife that's in front of you.
Turn right and take a step to your right then walk to the window and turn left then walk to the left side of the stove that's off to your left.
Open the cupboard that's above the left side of the microwave then put the knife in the green cup.
Pick up the green cup with the knife in it and close the cupboard..
Take a few steps to your right to face the coffee maker.
Put the cup under and to the left of the credit card that's in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on the counter.
